- `publish/show_notes.md` – timestamped sections based on the clean transcript and the verified URLs.
- `publish/episode_description.md` – episode summary under 180 words.
- `publish/launch_posts.md` – exactly two short standalone public launch posts (one key takeaway, one discussion question), written as broadcast messages with no @mentions or reply-style phrasing.

